title: Rose
description:
Rose is the youngest daughter of Bornian’s family. To avoid poverty, the grandmother sells her daughter and granddaughters one by one. Mr. X has bought and will take Rose after she is seventeen years old. A few months before her seventeenth birthday, Rose followed her sisters stealing diamonds.
